title: Soldier Killed in Iraq Raid Belonged to Delta Force
text:
Soldier Killed in Iraq Raid Belonged ... Soldier Killed in Iraq Raid Belonged to Delta Force There are 1 comment on the Yahoo! story from 12 hrs ago, titled Soldier Killed in Iraq Raid Belonged to Delta Force . In it, Yahoo! reports that: 
On Friday, October 23rd, Defense Secretary Ash Carter gave details about the Delta Force raid that freed hostages of Isis in Iraq. Carter spoke of the death of Master Sergeant Joshua L. Wheeler, the first American to die in direct combat with Isis. Join the discussion below, or Read more at Yahoo!.
